paragraphs.text:
val jvmText = sc.textFile("/home/tuxtor/Downloads/jvm2021.csv")

case class Answer(timestamp: String, age: String, jvmDev: String, jvmProd: String, version: String, ide: String, objective: String, jvmLanguages: String, otherLanguages: String, frameworks: String, server: String, containers:String, osDev:String, osProd: String, role: String, comment:String)

val jvm = jvmText.map(s => s.split(";")).filter(s => s(0) != "\"Timestamp\"").map(
    s => Answer(s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), s(1).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
            s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(3).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(4).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(5).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(6).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(7).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(8).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(9).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(10).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(11).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(12).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(13).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(14).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            ""
        )
).toDF()
jvm.registerTempTable("jvm")
